snippet.title: Moviehouse | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Moviehouse on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1576280/Moviehouse/

Moviehouse is a game about managing your own movie studio! Hire talent, write scripts and shoot the movie of your dreams, all the while balancing the whims of your fans and critics. 

Want more? 
Official Website: https://moviehousegame.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/anOdysseyStudio
Discord: https://discord.gg/fFTQFyphEa
Reddit: https://reddit.com/r/MoviehouseGame


#Moviehouse #tycoon #gameplay
